 What Where Find Jobs Advanced Job Search ITAM Analyst Capgemini 8,255 reviews Sparks Glencoe, MD Capgemini 8,255 reviews Read what people are saying about working here. Job details Job Type Contract Full Job Description Duration :12+Months 
Responsibilities : 
Track and report on all hardware and software across a network or enterprise; monitor and report on unlicensed installations and prohibited software. 
Define asset tracking processes, policies, and procedures. 
Ensure that all hardware and software assets are recorded, tracked and monitor terms and conditions of software license usage. 
Manage software assets to ensure license compliance. 
Participate in integrating asset management with other business functions and systems. 
Implement and refine repeatable processes and controls that demonstrate quality and regulatory compliance. 
Review inventory (physical and automated) for variances with Asset database records. 
Assess and provide variance resolution 
Analyze all variances and make recommendations to perform inventory 
Associate variances with other process areas and advise appropriate process manager 
Identify areas of process improvement and communicate to Asset Manager. 
Provide assistance and information to procurement 
Recommend and initiate end of life on high maintenance assets Perform other duties as assigned. 
